ck\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juni 20, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104cst1665702570102.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/cst1665702570102.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/cst1665702570102.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"cst1665702570102\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"cst1665702570102__ldircreate_224640\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Create the specified directory in the working directory, ignoring redirections in the assignment file.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"cst1665702570102__topic_d73652e1_d73653e1_d73654e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cst1665702570102__p_d73655e1_d73656e1_d73657e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">ldircreate</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">NewDirPath</var>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"cst1665702570102__section_w1637ab1b7b5_w1638ab1b7_w1639ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cst1665702570102__p_d73658e1_d73659e1_d73660e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">ldircreate \"exports\"</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cst1665702570102__topic_d48437e1_d48438e1_d48439e1_d48440e1_d48441e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d123170e77\">\n                       Parameters</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"cst1665702570102__d5988e20\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"cst1665702570102__d5988e20__entry__1\">Parameter</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"cst1665702570102__d5988e20__entry__2\">Data Type</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"cst1665702570102__d5988e20__entry__3\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cst1665702570102__d5988e20__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">NewDirPath</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cst1665702570102__d5988e20__entry__2\">String </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cst1665702570102__d5988e20__entry__3\">Directory name, optionally preceded by the\n\t\t\t\t path to the directory, which can be in a zip archive. Must end with a directory separator.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cst1665702570102__topic_d48442e1_d48443e1_d48444e1_d48445e1_d48446e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d123170e131\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"cst1665702570102__table_d6362e1_d6363e1_d6364e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"cst1665702570102__table_d6362e1_d6363e1_d6364e1__entry__1\">Value </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"cst1665702570102__table_d6362e1_d6363e1_d6364e1__entry__2\">Error constant </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"cst1665702570102__table_d6362e1_d6363e1_d6364e1__entry__3\">Meaning</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cst1665702570102__table_d6362e1_d6363e1_d6364e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cst1665702570102__table_d6362e1_d6363e1_d6364e1__entry__2\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cst1665702570102__table_d6362e1_d6363e1_d6364e1__entry__3\">Successful</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cst1665702570102__table_d6362e1_d6363e1_d6364e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-13</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cst1665702570102__table_d6362e1_d6363e1_d6364e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UIOSERR_OS_COMMAND&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cst1665702570102__table_d6362e1_d6363e1_d6364e1__entry__3\">An error occurred while trying to perform the\n                     OS command. Set <code class=\"ph codeph\">/pri=64</code> to display the exact error in the\n                     message frame.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cst1665702570102__topic_d48447e1_d48448e1_d48449e1_d48450e1_d48451e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d123170e218\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cst1665702570102__d5916e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cst1665702570102__topic_d48452e1_d48453e1_d48454e1_d48455e1_d48456e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d123170e227\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cst1665702570102__p_d73676e1_d73677e1_d73678e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">ldircreate</span> statement creates the specified directory in the current working directory, ignoring any file redirections in the assignment file. In other respects, it works the same as <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">dircreate</span>. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wnk1719404401528.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wnk1719404401528.html\" title=\"Create the specified directory in the working directory.\">dircreate</a>.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bau1719406118842.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>ProcScript for File System Management</a><p>Uniface provides ProcScript statements and functions for managing local files and directories.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526599\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526599\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "ldircreate Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juni 20, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Create the specified directory in the working directory, ignoring redirections in the assignment file. ldircreate NewDirPath Example: ldircreate \"exports\" Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description NewDirPath String Directory name, optionally preceded by the path to the directory, which can be in a zip archive. Must end with a directory separator. Return Values Table 2. Values returned by $procerror Value Error constant Meaning 0 Successful -13 <UIOSERR_OS_COMMAND> An error occurred while trying to perform the OS command. Set /pri=64 to display the exact error in the message frame. Use Allowed in all component types. Description The ldircreate statement creates the specified directory in the current working directory, ignoring any file redirections in the assignment file. In other respects, it works the same as dircreate . For more information, see dircreate . Related Links ProcScript for File System Management Uniface provides ProcScript statements and functions for managing local files and directories. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}